title: Turkish Noahs Ark Pudding Asure
description: Noah's ark pudding is a cornucopia of healthy ingredients such as dried fruits, legumes, and whole-grain wheat that are sweetened with sugar and fruit juices and cooked all together in one pot.

title: Yaprak Sarma
description: Yaprak sarma is a traditional dish in Turkey that is typically grape vine leaves rolled and filled with minced meat.
